      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_033_000046",
    "sentence": "蕭退",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_004_033_000047",
    "sentence": "蕭退，梁武帝弟司空鄱陽王恢之子也。",
    "entities": [
